==English==
===Adjective===
'''Fortunate'''
# Coming by good [[luck]] or favorable [[chance]]; 
# bringing some good thing not foreseen as certain; 
# presaging [[happiness]];
# [[auspicious]]
#: a '''fortunate''' [[event]]
#: a '''fortunate''' [[concurrence]] of [[circumstances]]
#: a '''fortunate''' [[investment]].
# Receiving same unforeseen or unexpected good, or some good which was not dependent on one's own skill or efforts 
# [[lucky]], favored by [[fortune]]

